Models

Community

Fields

Name Type Attributes Required Comment
id String
  • @id
  • @default(cuid())
 Yes The CUID of the community.
createdAt DateTime
  • @default(now())
 Yes When the community was created.
updatedAt DateTime
  • @default(now())
  • @updatedAt
 Yes When the community database entry was last updated.
name String
  • @unique
  • @default()
 Yes Name used in URL to find community, always lower case to prevent issues.
display_name String
  • @unique
  • @default()
 Yes Name shown anywhere other than the URL, can contain upper case letters since it is not used for identification.
description String
  • @default(This community doesn't have a description.)
 Yes Description of the community.
rules String[]
  • @default([])
 Yes Rules of the community.
image String
  • @default(/images/favicon/favicon.svg)
 Yes Image that is shown for the community, defaults to the favicon.
bg_image String
  • @default(/images/default_community_bg.png)
 Yes -
public Boolean
  • @default(true)
 Yes If false, this community cannot be accessed and will not be shown. Currently unimplemented.
admin_ids String[]
  • @default([])
 Yes User CUIDS of the community administrator(s).
admins CommunityAdminship[]
  • -
Yes -
memberships CommunityMembership[]
  • -
Yes -
sidebar_md String
  • @default()
 Yes Deprecated, do not use.
posts Post[]
  • -
Yes Relation to all posts in this community.

    // ... provide filter here
  }
})

Fields

Name Type Attributes Required Comment
id String
  • @id
  • @default(cuid())
 Yes The CUID of the user.
github_id Int?
  • @unique
 No -
email String?
  • @unique
 No The user's email. If possible, do not leave empty (OAuth however may not provide an email, so this has to be made "optional").
emailVerified DateTime?
  • -
No When the user verified their email, currently unimplemented.
emailLastUpdate DateTime?
  • -
No When the user last updated their email.
username String
  • @unique
 Yes The user's username.
usernameLastUpdate DateTime?
  • -
No When the user last updated their username.
description String
  • @default(This user has not set their description.)
 Yes The users description, displayed on their profile and when a user hovers over their username.
password_hash String?
  • -
No The user's password.
createdAt DateTime
  • @default(now())
 Yes When the user was created.
updatedAt DateTime
  • @updatedAt
 Yes When the user database entry was last updated.
name String?
  • -
No Deprecated, do not use.
profile_image String
  • @default(/images/favicon/favicon.svg)
 Yes Deprecated, do not use.
image String?
  • -
No The profile image of the user.
posts Post[]
  • -
Yes All posts made by the user.
public Boolean
  • @default(true)
 Yes Whether the user profile and posts are public.
savedPosts String[]
  • @default([])
 Yes Posts saved by the user.
memberships CommunityMembership[]
  • -
Yes Communities the user is a member of.
adminships CommunityAdminship[]
  • -
Yes Communities the user is an admin of.

  • -
Yes -

  • -
Yes -

  • -

  • -

  • -

  • -

  • -
